  <!-- Help Window -->
  <StyleExpand_HelpTitle>RimTalk 文风扩展 - 帮助</StyleExpand_HelpTitle>
  <StyleExpand_HelpQuickStart>== 快速开始 ==</StyleExpand_HelpQuickStart>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStep1>1. 将 .txt 文件放入 Styles 文件夹（点击"打开文件夹"）</StyleExpand_HelpStep1>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStep2>2. 点击"扫描文风"检测新文件</StyleExpand_HelpStep2>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStep3>3. 从列表中选择一个文风</StyleExpand_HelpStep3>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStep4>4. 点击"切分文风"处理文风</StyleExpand_HelpStep4>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStep5>5. 完成！文风将用于 RimTalk 对话</StyleExpand_HelpStep5>
  <StyleExpand_HelpApiConfig>== API 配置 ==</StyleExpand_HelpApiConfig>
  <StyleExpand_HelpApiUrl>- 向量 API 地址：你的 embedding API 端点</StyleExpand_HelpApiUrl>
  <StyleExpand_HelpApiSupport>- 支持 OpenAI 兼容的 API（Ollama、OpenAI 等）</StyleExpand_HelpApiSupport>
  <StyleExpand_HelpApiModel>- 模型：embedding 模型名称（如 bge-small-zh）</StyleExpand_HelpApiModel>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleFiles>== 文风文件 ==</StyleExpand_HelpStyleFiles>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleOne>- 一个 .txt 文件 = 一种文风</StyleExpand_HelpStyleOne>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleName>- 文件名即文风名</StyleExpand_HelpStyleName>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleContent>- 文件内容用作文风示例</StyleExpand_HelpStyleContent>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleSize>- 推荐字数：中文 5,000-50,000 字 | 英文 3,000-30,000 词</StyleExpand_HelpStyleSize>
  <StyleExpand_HelpStyleSizeNote>- 更大的文件可用但处理时间更长</StyleExpand_HelpStyleSizeNote>
  <StyleExpand_HelpChunking>== 切分 ==</StyleExpand_HelpChunking>
  <StyleExpand_HelpChunkWhat>- 将文本切分成较小的片段</StyleExpand_HelpChunkWhat>
  <StyleExpand_HelpChunkEmbed>- 为每个片段计算 embedding</StyleExpand_HelpChunkEmbed>
  <StyleExpand_HelpChunkCache>- 结果缓存以加快加载</StyleExpand_HelpChunkCache>
  <StyleExpand_HelpAdvanced>== 高级模式 ==</StyleExpand_HelpAdvanced>
